# opencoo .dockerignore — engine image (PR-X2, phase-a follow-up).
#
# Inclusion-by-exclusion approach: we exclude everything that the build
# stages don't need or that absolutely must not ship in a published image
# (secrets, partner-private docs, .git history, test fixtures).
#
# Belt-and-braces against .gitignore: docker build uses THIS file, not
# .gitignore. A file gitignored from the public repo (architecture.md,
# docs/local/) is still on disk in the maintainer's worktree and would
# be tar-streamed into the build context unless this file blocks it.

# --- Version control + IDE + tooling state ---
.git
.gitattributes
.github
.husky
.claude
.agents
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store

# --- Build outputs + dependency state (re-built inside the image) ---
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
build
**/build
**/.turbo
**/.tsbuildinfo
**/.tsbuildinfo.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
**/.vitest

# --- Tests + fixtures (build stage runs `pnpm build`, not `pnpm test`;
#     fixtures inflate the build context for zero runtime value) ---
tests
**/__fixtures__
**/__snapshots__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
**/playwright.config.ts
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/vitest.config.ts
vitest.config.ts
vitest.injection.config.ts
vitest.e2e.config.ts
vitest.live-pilot.config.ts

# --- Local dev compose + env (image runtime ships its own envs) ---
compose.yml
compose.e2e.yml
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Internal / partner-private docs (CLAUDE.md "Do not publish ...
#     filenames from docs/local/ in any public artifact") ---
architecture.md
DECISIONS.md
docs/local
docs/plan-appendix
docs/pilot-runbook.md

# --- Public spec / planning docs (no value at runtime; if devops needs
#     a doc baked into the image, the image is the wrong place — link
#     to the GitHub repo) ---
THREAT-MODEL.md
PRD.md
IMPLEMENTATION-PLAN.md
CHANGES-v0.1.md
CONVENTIONS.md
CLAUDE.md
README.md
LICENSE.md
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md
docs/decisions-resolved.md
docs/threat-model-signoff-*.md

# --- Design system (only ships in the UI dist, which the build stage
#     writes into packages/engine-self-operating/dist/ui already) ---
design_system
diagrams

# --- Misc artifacts ---
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
.npmrc.local
**/Dockerfile
**/docker-compose.yml
**/.dockerignore
deploy
scripts/regen-injection-fixtures.ts
skills-lock.json
